    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔认为巴塞尔协议 III 的修订取得了进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-sees-progress-on-changes-to-basel-iii-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，巴塞尔协议 III 修订提案将在大约 60 天内公布，供大家评论。鲍威尔在参议院银行、住房和城市事务委员会作证时发表了上述言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-sees-progress-on-changes-to-basel-iii-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:15:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称更多良好通胀数据将增强美联储信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-says-more-good-inflation-data-would-strengthen-fed-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，最近的数据表明物价“进一步温和上涨”，但“更多好数据”将增强人们对通胀正在向美联储 2% 目标下降的信心。鲍威尔在参议院银行、住房和城市事务委员会作证时发表了上述讲话（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-says-more-good-inflation-data-would-strengthen-fed-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:09:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林德纳的欧洲央行危机工具引发政策制定者担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lindner-s-ecb-crisis-tool-doubts-stoke-dismay-among-policymakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 公开表达了对欧洲央行向法国提供危机援助的合法性的怀疑，这让欧洲决策圈感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lindner-s-ecb-crisis-tool-doubts-stoke-dismay-among-policymakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>知情人士透露，图利普·西迪克将出任英国城市事务大臣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命图利普·西迪克 (Tulip Siddiq) 为英国金融城大臣，该职位属于财政部，将让她成为监管和倡导关键金融服务行业的核心人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国下一届政府将继承强劲增长势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-next-government-is-set-to-inherit-resilient-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国经济今年预计将保持稳定增长，这将缓解下届政府面临的预算挑战。此前，法国提前大选导致出现悬浮议会，未来财政政策面临巨大不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-next-government-is-set-to-inherit-resilient-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙影业因与 Skydance 达成交易面临被穆迪评级降至垃圾级的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/paramount-may-get-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s-after-skydance-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在派拉蒙全球同意出售给天舞传媒 (Skydance Media) 后，该公司的信用评级可能被穆迪评级下调至垃圾级，该债券评级机构指出派拉蒙业务面临“巨大的长期压力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/paramount-may-get-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s-after-skydance-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
